text:

name: businessinsider
text: Numerous people said SoulCycle didn't discipline or fire misbehaving instructors because they were moneymakers, and instead lavished them with perks like Soho House memberships and, in one case, a loaner Mercedes-Benz. https://t.co/NerTS9VlR2

text:

name: businessinsider
text:
